{"tid":340444,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[懷舊撚] 寶物沉歸底 50-70年代香港生活舊照","createTime":"2017-07-30T02:56:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T08:49:08.000Z","uid":88392,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9ccb91e763600c345504cbf3960696f14701b717","tid":340444,"uid":88392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T02:56:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>話說近日我屋企嘅老人家要搬屋，清咗好多垃圾<br />\n咁做不孝孫當然上去尋寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n發現佢屋企收埋咗一大罐舊相，全部係兩老當年拍拖到生B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有一大堆唔知邊位嘅相片，索性全數充公打算一代傳一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\n有見及此，我打算三不五時搵啲貼上嚟分享吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知有無懷舊撚有興趣睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/105342_9734dad123f5b0d9a8b0838fe7047460.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F105342_9734dad123f5b0d9a8b0838fe7047460.jpg&h=9a049e3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/105239_cc2c3622fa258a580af1b3e8b50b6d9b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F105239_cc2c3622fa258a580af1b3e8b50b6d9b.jpg&h=1c636778&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/105240_5ec2f536a7a7ca6d2ccf230e8ba34fa3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F105240_5ec2f536a7a7ca6d2ccf230e8ba34fa3.jpg&h=689be120&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/105243_52d39fcd8c42d8f4c7732929586bd3b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F105243_52d39fcd8c42d8f4c7732929586bd3b0.j